1. 	Service definition and description

"User experience improvement plan" is a service function we proposed for lenovo mobile devices, which is designed to enhance the products or services and improve the user experience. After enabling the "User experience improvement plan" function in your mobile device, you can have the priority to experience the new services of "User experience improvement plan" while using the original functions of your mobile devices: 

 	Enhanced device hardware and software acceleration function and personalized experience
 (1) Speed up the boot process and save your boot time to provide you with a better boot experience;
 (2) Provide you with the most popular software function experience. These functions are simple, easy to use and considerate;
 (3) Enhanced GPS positioning function, providing faster and more accurate GPS positioning functions;
 (4) Intelligent recognition and switching functions of 3G, WLAN and other network modes provide personalized services in different network environments. This largely save your 3G network traffic and costs while you enjoy the services; 

 	Multi-faceted, personalized content recommendation service:
 (1) When you are playing games, we will provide you with the latest game download links and information that you may be interested in;
 (2) When you are listening to music, we will provide you with information on recent activities, concerts and popular new songs of related singers;
 (3) When you are trying to use mobile offices, we will provide you with the latest and most popular office software and experience;
 (4) When you are surfing the Web, we will provide you with safe and fast access experience, and recommend the latest software, games, news, ebooks, music, videos and other personalized content services and multimedia audio-visual entertainment that you may be interested in;
 (5) When you are positioning navigation, in addition to the more accurate and efficient GPS positioning functions, we will also provide you with food, clothing and shelter recommendations and retrieval services based on location information;

 	Safe and reliable software and service experiences;
 (1) Through the grading and scoring mechanism for software, we will provide you with many types of built-in software which are more secure;
 (2) Considerate one-stop application retrieve, download, install and uninstall services, letting you experience the most popular software and games immediately;
 (3) Build personal cloud storage services for you; Let you share information between phones, computers, pads and even multimedia televisions of compatible formats anywhere, and you will no longer need to worry about missing your files. 
